             <div class="media-body">
              <h3>
               2018 UNC Charlotte Conference on Writing Studies
              </h3>
              <i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-calendar">
              </i>
              <span class="date-display-single">
               July 26, 2018
              </span>
              <br/>
              <p>
               The UNC Charlotte Conference on Writing Studies took place October 19, 2018 at Center City.  For information on the 2019 Conference, go to
               <a href="https://pages.uncc.edu/writingconference/">
                https://pages.uncc.edu/writingconference/
               </a>
               . New information will be added as we get closer to fall 2019.
              </p>
              <p>
              </p>
